:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Immensely helpful!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504038003-->
::::'''Damionis:''' That's good to hear. I've always felt somewhat guilty toward you, so knowing I've been able to help eases my mind.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's not a big deal.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504038005-->
::::'''Damionis:''' In that case, I've always felt a certain guilt toward you. If there's anything you need help with, please don't hesitate to ask.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504038006-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504038006-->
:::'''Damionis:''' Though Lady Aglaea has forbidden me from further exploring the world beyond the sky, my curiosity remains unabated. If you're interested, feel free to chat with me anytime.
