:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_830110146-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_830110146-->
:::'''Damionis:''' I already have an ideal route to go around the city walls. Let's set off now.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's go!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_803010101_67-->
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: OpenActivityUI-->
:::{{DIcon|Exit}} Maybe later.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_830110149-->
